{"name":"Randy Phalla's Portfolio Website","short_name":"RP Portfolio","description":"I’m a Front-end Developer and Designer based in London, Ontario Canada. I am passionate about creating aesthetically websites and designs. I can translate your artwork files (Photoshop, Illustrator, Sketch, Figma, etc.) and prototype them into web or mobile using HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript. I’m currently working at Devlift Media as a Web Developer, building websites and mobile apps with the latest web technologies such as HTML5, CSS3 (SCSS), JavaScript (ES5/6), TypeScript, Angular, Ionic, ReactJS and React Native.","start_url":"/","background_color":"#FFFFFF","theme_color":"#FF001F","display":"standalone","cacheDigest":"e5a34021602099216a533edae145fc02","icons":[{"src":"icons/icon-48x48.png?v=e5a34021602099216a533edae145fc02","sizes":"48x48","type":"image/png"},{"src":"icons/icon-72x72.png?v=e5a34021602099216a533edae145fc02","sizes":"72x72","type":"image/png"},{"src":"icons/icon-96x96.png?v=e5a34021602099216a533edae145fc02","sizes":"96x96","type":"image/png"},{"src":"icons/icon-144x144.png?v=e5a34021602099216a533edae145fc02","sizes":"144x144","type":"image/png"},{"src":"icons/icon-192x192.png?v=e5a34021602099216a533edae145fc02","sizes":"192x192","type":"image/png"},{"src":"icons/icon-256x256.png?v=e5a34021602099216a533edae145fc02","sizes":"256x256","type":"image/png"},{"src":"icons/icon-384x384.png?v=e5a34021602099216a533edae145fc02","sizes":"384x384","type":"image/png"},{"src":"icons/icon-512x512.png?v=e5a34021602099216a533edae145fc02","sizes":"512x512","type":"image/png"}]}